des:
Learn about Witlingo by asking questions on our products Buildlingo and Castlingo, when the company was founded, and who the teammates are.

Witlingo is a McLean, Virginia based company focused on building products and solutions that make it easier for companies and organizations of all sizes to deliver Voice First experiences with minimal effort and cost.

This skill was built using Buildlingo, a Witlingo product. If you would like your very own Buildlingo skill, please visit http://www.witlingo.com/buildlingo/
